biography: Udom Taepanich (Thai: อุดม แต้พานิช), also known by the nickname Nose (Thai: โน๊ต), is a stand-up comedian, artist and writer. He was named as One of the best Persons of the Century in Performing Arts by Nation Publishing Group in 2000. He is well known as Diew 1-11 (Stand Up Comedy).
name: Udom Taepanich
